Change Point Report

Dataset: Application_3.1.csv

  • The processed data contains annual max streamflow measurements between 1909 and 2018.
  • There are 110 values in the dataset, 1 of which are missing.

Exploratory Data Analysis

Mann-Whitney-Pettitt Test

Purpose: Detect abrupt changes in the annual max streamflow data.

Result: There is a significant abrupt change point in 1974.

Mann-Kendall-Sneyers Test

Purpose: Detect the beginning of a change in trend in the annual max streamflow data.

Result: There are no significant trend changes.
